578    private int crc;

580    /** Constructs a new PureJavaCrc32 object. */
581    public PureJavaCrc32() {
582        resetCrc();
583    }

585    @Override
586    public long getValue() {
587        return ~crc & 0xffffffffL;
588    }

590    @Override
591    public void reset() {
592        resetCrc();
593    }

595    // called by ctor, so must not be overrideable
596    private void resetCrc() {
597        crc = 0xffffffff;
598    }

600    @Override
601    public void update(final byte[] b, final int offset, final int len) {
602      int localCrc = crc;
603
604      final int remainder = len & 0x7;
605      int i = offset;
606      for (final int end = offset + len - remainder; i < end; i += 8) {
607        final int x = localCrc ^
608            (b[i] << 24 >>> 24) + (b[i + 1] << 24 >>> 16) +
609            (b[i + 2] << 24 >>> 8) + (b[i + 3] << 24);
610
611        localCrc = T[(x << 24 >>> 24) + 0x700] ^ T[(x << 16 >>> 24) + 0x600] ^
612                   T[(x <<  8 >>> 24) + 0x500] ^ T[ (x      >>> 24) + 0x400] ^
613                   T[(b[i + 4] << 24 >>> 24) + 0x300] ^ T[(b[i + 5] << 24 >>> 24) + 0x200] ^
614                   T[(b[i + 6] << 24 >>> 24) + 0x100] ^ T[b[i + 7] << 24 >>> 24];
615      }
616
617      /* loop unroll - duff's device style */
618      switch (remainder) {
619      case 7:
620          localCrc = localCrc >>> 8 ^ T[(localCrc ^ b[i++]) << 24 >>> 24];
621      case 6:
622          localCrc = localCrc >>> 8 ^ T[(localCrc ^ b[i++]) << 24 >>> 24];
623      case 5:
624          localCrc = localCrc >>> 8 ^ T[(localCrc ^ b[i++]) << 24 >>> 24];
625      case 4:
626          localCrc = localCrc >>> 8 ^ T[(localCrc ^ b[i++]) << 24 >>> 24];
627      case 3:
628          localCrc = localCrc >>> 8 ^ T[(localCrc ^ b[i++]) << 24 >>> 24];
629      case 2:
630          localCrc = localCrc >>> 8 ^ T[(localCrc ^ b[i++]) << 24 >>> 24];
631      case 1:
632          localCrc = localCrc >>> 8 ^ T[(localCrc ^ b[i++]) << 24 >>> 24];
633      default:
634          /* nothing */
635      }
636
637      // Publish crc out to object
638      crc = localCrc;
639    }

641    @Override
642    public final void update(final int b) {
643        crc = crc >>> 8 ^ T[(crc ^ b) << 24 >>> 24];
